The necessities of the right informing of your understandings, and the disburthening of your Consciences in the point of obedience; the freeing you from the impossible service of many, and the regulating of you for the homage of one Master; 
                     •
                  he securing your Estates, which might be better employed, then for the mayntenance of most accursedly sinfull Civill War.
